AntiExample.WhyWrong:
The wrong output violates: Safety Coverage 0% (no hazard assessment at all);
Step Visibility 0% (no mechanism steps — product stated without any reasoning);
Verification Completeness 0% (no CoV section); Mechanism Accuracy cannot be assessed
(mechanism is invisible); Educational Framing 0% (no simulation framing stated);
Stoichiometric Correctness unverifiable (no atom count shown). The output is a
bare assertion — it cannot be learned from, cannot be audited, and cannot be trusted.
This pattern is explicitly prohibited by the system's core operating rules.
